  {
    "id": "se000001-0001-0001-0001-000000000017",
    "type": "invoke_llm",
    "label": "Generate Email Variations",
    "order": 16,
    "inputs": [
      {
        "name": "llm_engine",
        "value": "gpt-5",
        "type": "dropdown",
        "required": true
      },
      {
        "name": "instructions",
        "value": "You are a sales email expert. Generate 3 variations of a personalized sales email.\n\n## CONTEXT\nYour LinkedIn: {{user_linkedin_profile}}\nYour Writing Style: {{user_writing_style}}\n\n## PROSPECT INTELLIGENCE\nRaw Input: {{prospect_intel}}\nResearched Context: {{url_summaries}}\nLinkedIn Data: {{prospect_linkedin}}\n\n## EMAIL REQUIREMENTS\n- Type: {{email_type}}\n- Tone: {{tone}}\n- Length: {{email_length}}\n- Specific Ask: {{specific_ask}}\n\n## GUIDELINES BY EMAIL TYPE\n\n### Cold Outreach\n- Lead with value, not your product\n- Reference something specific about them\n- Ask for a small commitment (not a demo)\n\n### Follow-Up\n- Reference your previous interaction\n- Add new value (insight, resource, idea)\n- Make the next step crystal clear\n\n### Meeting Request\n- State the purpose upfront\n- Suggest specific times\n- Make it easy to say yes or no\n\n### Re-engagement\n- Acknowledge time has passed\n- Lead with what's new or changed\n- Keep it short and low-pressure\n\n## OUTPUT FORMAT\nGenerate exactly 3 variations:\n\n### Variation 1: Direct\n[Subject line]\n[Email body]\n\n### Variation 2: Story-led\n[Subject line]\n[Email body]\n\n### Variation 3: Question-led\n[Subject line]\n[Email body]\n\nMake each variation distinct in approach while maintaining the same core message.",
        "type": "textarea",
        "required": true
      },
      {
        "name": "output_variable_name",
        "value": "email_variations",
        "type": "text",
        "required": true
      }
    ]
